                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">Minimum distance</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 whitespace-nowrap">5 km</td>
                  <td class="py-2">The floor a launched pilot is scored at, even if they land sooner ("bomb-out points").</td>
