                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 whitespace-nowrap">On</td>
                  <td class="py-2">Rewards leading at the front of the pack. On for both categories in the FAI formula (paragliding weights them higher, as it has no arrival term).</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-border/50">
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">Leading formula</td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 whitespace-nowrap">Per sport</td>
                  <td class="py-2">The leading-coefficient variant (<SpecRef section="11.3.1" label="§11.3.1" />): <strong>classic</strong> (squared-distance) for hang gliding, <strong>weighted</strong> (weighted-area, GAP2020+) for paragliding — the 2024 spec pairing. Either can be selected for any competition.</td>
