                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">
                    <a href="#leading-weight" class="underline hover:text-foreground">PG leading weight</a>
                  </td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 whitespace-nowrap">S7F 2024</td>
                  <td class="py-2">Paragliding only: the leading↔time weight split. New PG comps default to <strong>S7F 2024</strong> (the LeadingTimeRatio parameter, default 26%); comps created before 15 July 2026 default to <strong>GAP2020</strong> (AirScore parity) so their scores don't shift. No effect on hang gliding.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-border/50">
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4">
                    <a href="#distance-origin" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Distance origin</a>
                  </td>
                  <td class="py-2 pr-4 whitespace-nowrap">Take-off</td>
                  <td class="py-2">Scored distance is measured from the take-off point through the start (FAI CIVL GAP / PWCA). "Start cylinder" excludes the take-off→start leg (HGFA/SAFA).</td>
