          </div>

          <div id="defaults-hg" class="ml-2 scroll-mt-20">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Hang gliding (HG)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-1 ml-2">
              <li><a href="#arrival-points" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Arrival points</a>: <strong>on</strong> — HG scores order of arrival at ESS (<SpecRef section="11.4" label="§11.4" />).</li>
              <li><a href="#distance-difficulty" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Distance difficulty</a>: <strong>on</strong> — HG distance points are half linear, half difficulty (<SpecRef section="11.1.1" label="§11.1.1" />).</li>
              <li><a href="#leading-points" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Leading coefficient</a>: <strong>classic</strong> (squared-distance) with the <strong>5/6</strong> time-points exponent — the 2024-spec hang-gliding pairing (<SpecRef section="11.2" label="§11.2" />, <SpecRef section="11.3.1" label="§11.3.1" />).</li>
              <li>Jump-the-gun (early start, <SpecRef section="12.2" label="§12.2" />): 1 penalty point per <strong>2 s</strong> early, up to <strong>300 s</strong> before minimum distance only.</li>
              <li>ESS but not goal (<SpecRef section="12.1" label="§12.1" />): keeps <strong>80%</strong> of time and arrival points — the spec's recommended default, overridable by local regulations.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div id="defaults-pg" class="ml-2 scroll-mt-20">
            <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-1">Paragliding (PG)</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-muted-foreground space-y-1 ml-2">
              <li><a href="#arrival-points" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Arrival points</a>: <strong>off</strong> — paragliding has no arrival term in the spec.</li>
              <li><a href="#distance-difficulty" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Distance difficulty</a>: <strong>off</strong> — paragliding distance is always the pure-linear proportion.</li>
              <li><a href="#leading-points" class="underline hover:text-foreground">Leading coefficient</a>: <strong>weighted</strong> (weighted-area) with the <strong>5/6</strong> time-points exponent — the 2024-spec paragliding pairing (<SpecRef section="11.2" label="§11.2" />, <SpecRef section="11.3.1" label="§11.3.1" />).</li>
              <li>Early starts are scored launch→start (no jump-the-gun penalty; that is HG-only).</li>
              <li>ESS but not goal (<SpecRef section="12.1" label="§12.1" />): <strong>0%</strong> — no goal, no time points. Fixed by the spec (it discourages high-speed final glides low to the ground) and not configurable for paragliding.</li>
            </ul>
